00:58:07,980 --> 00:58:09,510
(Chatter continues)

998
00:58:15,390 --> 00:58:17,290
Get on out of here!

999
00:58:17,560 --> 00:58:18,620
What the hell
are you doing?

1000
00:58:18,860 --> 00:58:20,790
- Get back.
- Hey!

1001
00:58:21,130 --> 00:58:22,930
You better pick up
your sheets and run!

1002
00:58:23,230 --> 00:58:24,730
- (Gunshot)
- <i>(crowd screams)</i>

1003
00:58:26,700 --> 00:58:28,600
Get out of here.
I'm gonna get you!

1004
00:58:28,870 --> 00:58:30,170
Bessie:
<i>Get out of here!</i>

1005
00:58:31,640 --> 00:58:35,570
<i>We'll be back!</i>
<i>(Cackles)</i>

