1109
01:06:13,930 --> 01:06:16,370
Man:
<i>Whoo-hoo!</i>

1110
01:06:16,600 --> 01:06:18,100
<i>Morning, Gee!</i>

1111
01:06:19,940 --> 01:06:21,500
I got something for you.

1112
01:06:27,380 --> 01:06:29,410
Got somebody I want
you to meet.

1113
01:06:29,650 --> 01:06:31,410
This here is Gertrude.

1114
01:06:31,720 --> 01:06:34,180
She's a singer.
Writes songs, too.

1115
01:06:38,660 --> 01:06:41,690
You know Claudine
dropped out in Cincinnati.

1116
01:06:41,890 --> 01:06:42,990
Got pregnant.

1117
01:06:43,330 --> 01:06:44,730
So I hired Gertrude
here to replace her.

1118
01:06:45,060 --> 01:06:47,130
What the fuck you showing her
to me for?

1119
01:06:48,330 --> 01:06:49,570
I don't know.

1120
01:06:49,900 --> 01:06:51,770
Thought maybe you might
have something to say.

1121
01:06:52,000 --> 01:06:53,200
Sort of like "welcome."

1122
01:06:53,540 --> 01:06:56,070
What kind of fucked-up name
is Gertrude?

1123
01:06:56,410 --> 01:06:57,840
- You a half-breed?
- Excuse us, please.

1124
01:06:58,180 --> 01:07:00,140
Go on and get yourself
something to eat, baby.

1125
01:07:03,180 --> 01:07:04,150
What the hell
is wrong with you?

1126
01:07:04,420 --> 01:07:05,580
I know you got your
side pieces,

1127
01:07:05,880 --> 01:07:07,280
but why you gotta
rub 'em in my face?

1128
01:07:07,550 --> 01:07:08,320
I'm just trying
to build a--

