you've been sending.

1155
01:08:58,960 --> 01:09:03,270
They're nice,
feeding four kids and all.

1156
01:09:16,980 --> 01:09:18,610
Okay, look.

1157
01:09:18,980 --> 01:09:23,290
I know you and I bump heads
